{
  "id": "tpl_demo_agentbrowser_001",
  "name": "agent_browser_testing",
  "display_name": "智能浏览器自动测试",
  "description": "演示 Agent Browser 技能，使用 AI 驱动的浏览器自动化执行测试场景",
  "icon": "🤖",
  "category": "testing",
  "subcategory": "browser",
  "tags": ["agent", "browser", "automation", "e2e", "demo", "skill"],
  "project_type": "workflow",
  "prompt_template": "请帮我创建一个 AI 驱动的浏览器测试场景：\n\n**目标网站：** {{targetUrl}}\n**测试场景：** {{scenario}}\n**期望结果：** {{expectedResult}}\n\n**执行步骤：**\n\n### 步骤1：启动智能浏览器\n```\n/agent-browser navigate {{targetUrl}}\n```\n\n### 步骤2：执行测试场景\n```\n/agent-browser {{scenario}}\n```\n\n### 步骤3：验证结果\n对比实际结果与期望结果，截图记录。\n\n### 步骤4：生成测试报告\n```\n/memory-management save \"浏览器测试: {{targetUrl}} - {{scenario}}\"\n```\n\n**使用的技能：** agent-browser, memory-management",
  "variables_schema": [
    {
      "name": "targetUrl",
      "label": "目标网站",
      "type": "string",
      "required": true,
      "placeholder": "https://example.com"
    },
    {
      "name": "scenario",
      "label": "测试场景",
      "type": "select",
      "required": true,
      "options": [
        { "value": "login-flow", "label": "登录流程测试" },
        { "value": "form-submit", "label": "表单提交测试" },
        { "value": "navigation", "label": "导航测试" },
        { "value": "custom", "label": "自定义场景" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "expectedResult",
      "label": "期望结果",
      "type": "string",
      "required": false,
      "placeholder": "描述测试通过的标准"
    }
  ],
  "file_structure": {},
  "default_files": [],
  "is_builtin": true,
  "author": "ChainlessChain Team",
  "version": "1.0.0",
